<div class="row">
  <div class="col-sm-12">
    <h2>Contributions from multiple events</h2>
    <p class="terms">Use this form to bulk load historic records of contributions across multiple events and multiple dates. Or, <a href="/log-em">switch to log single events</a>.</p>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="row">
  <form id="contributionForm" method="post" action="/log-many">
    <input type="hidden" name="_csrf" value="{{{token}}}">
    <div class="col-sm-3">
      <h3>What</h3>
      {{> logging/select-teams}}
      {{> logging/select-type}}
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-9">
      <h3>Who, When, Description</h3>
      <ul class="small">
        <li>Copy and paste from your spreadsheet or CSV file</li>
        <li>One contribution per line</li>
        <li>FORMAT: email@address.com, yyyy-mm-dd, short description of the contribution activity</li>
        <li>Comma seperated</li>
        <li>Date must be formatted yyyy-mm-dd</li>
        <li>Straight quote marks (" and ') will be removed</li>
        <li>Don't worry about loading the same record twice (we won't double count it)</li>
      </ul>
      <textarea class="form-control" rows="12" name="contributors" wrap="off" required placeholder="email@address.com, yyyy-mm-dd, short description of the contribution activity"></textarea>
      {{> logging/clarify}}
      <br />
      {{> logging/evidence}}
      <br />
      <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Log these <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-ok-sign"></span></button>
    </div>
  </form>
</div>



